(16, 30, '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A native of Massachusetts, Patrick Cullen is a graduate of <em>The Catholic University</em> in Washington, D.C.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; He lives in Washington, D.C., and works in the theater there.</p>', '.png'),
